{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","t